{{monster info}}
==Useful Info==
'''Shadow imps''' are one of the flimsier [[tier-5 demon]]s. If found early, they can be significant threats due to their [[Pain]] spell. They usually only appear as part of certain [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|shadow imps will appear earlier in [[the Dungeon]]: on D:4-7 instead of D:5-8.}}
*Prior to [[0.30]], shadow imps could be created by [[Call Imp]].
*Prior to [[0.28]], shadow imps could [[see invisible]].
*Prior to [[0.17]], shadow imps could cast Animate Dead.
*Prior to [[0.12]], summoned shadow imps would cast Animate Dead, allowing characters with no [[Necromancy]] skill to generate armies of the dead.
